# https://w3id.org/MQTT4SSN-Ontology/ redirects via HTTP 303 using content negotiation:
# - HTML requests are redirected to:
#   https://doernern.github.io/MQTT4SSNOntology/documentation/index-en.html
# - RDF/OWL requests are redirected to:
#   https://doernern.github.io/MQTT4SSNOntology/documentation/ontology.owl

